            .bio.padding-bottom30
              p My name is Sydney Anh Mai and I am a product designer. If you don’t work in tech and wonder what that means, let’s just say I design human workflows on the web. My passion for workflow optimization, purposeful interactions, and stellar typography has taken me across industries and products — currently, Kickstarter. I believe that good designers understand the material of their design, be it paper, brick, or code.
              p.padding-top18 I was a bored communication major when I took my first web design class  — it changed my life. When I’m not building weird things in my free time, you can find me waddling at the beach, browsing videos of cats, Googling the <a class="text-link" href="https://www.google.com/search?sxsrf=ALeKk03yo2KwVBZvjAX1V6as7W_g2nQyuw:1621892956138&q=Bishkek&stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAONgVuLQz9U3MEy3jH_EaMwt8PLHPWEprUlrTl5jVOHiCs7IL3fNK8ksqRQS42KDsnikuLjgmngWsbI7ZRZnZKdmAwDUf6XJTAAAAA&biw=1282&bih=921" target="_blank">capital of Kyrgyzstan</a>, or resuscitating my many dying plants.
